a on bittorrent</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/simple-peer\">simple-peer</a> - send video/voice/data p2p in the browser (with webrtc)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/torrent-docker\">torrent-docker</a> - realtime boot of remote docker images over bittorrent</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/torrent-mount\">torrent-mount</a> - mount a torrent as a filesystem</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/webtorrent\">webtorrent</a> - streaming torrent client for node &#x26; the browser</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"browserify\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#browserify\" aria-label=\"browserify permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>browserify</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/brfs\">brfs</a> - turn <code class=\"language-text\">fs.readFileSync()</code> calls into inlined static assets</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/defunctzombie/4339901\">browser field spec</a> - replace certain files/modules when a module is bundled for the browser</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://npmjs.org/package/browserify\">browserify</a> - use <code class=\"language-text\">require()</code> in the browser</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/stackgl/glslify\">glslify</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/stackgl/glslify\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, 